data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with a spacious open foyer entrance, located near shopping stores and Restaurants. SELLER NOW OFFERING $8k FOR CLOSING COST. This well-maintained property boasts a range of impressive features that are sure to captivate any buyer. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open foyer that sets the tone for the entire home. The main living areas feature high-quality LVT waterproof vinyl plank flooring, offering both style and durability. State of the Art Entertainment Center creates a stunning appearance to view from the kitchen and dining room area. The kitchen features beautiful mahogany cabinets that provide ample storage and add a touch of elegance to the space and a generously sized food pantry, making it easy to keep your kitchen well-stocked and organized.  The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, which are not only aesthetically pleasing but also easy to maintain. Enhance your security and peace of mind with surveillance cameras strategically placed around the property. The air conditioning system has recently been upgraded with a brand-new compressor and motor, ensuring comfort and energy efficiency (Replaced in June 2023). The spacious bedrooms feature walk-in closets, providing ample storage space for your wardrobe and belongings. The Master Bathroom has a Bluetooth speaker inside the ventilation system.   This home offers the perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm. With its open layout, high-quality finishes, and recent AC system upgrade, it's ready to provide comfort and convenience to its new owners with no rear neighbors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Hurry and Schedule a viewing 7 days a week after 12pm only.
